{{Quote|Certainly people are always very envious of me. When I join a new theater company, the other actors look down the program, see my ''Return of the Jedi'' credit and say, 'Oh, you were part of ''Star Wars''.' I smile and say, 'Yes, but only for twenty-six and a half seconds.'|Caroline Blackiston|<ref name="The Women Of Star Wars">{{GalaxyCite|12|The Women Of Star Wars}}</ref>}}
'''Caroline Blakiston''' is a British actress who played [[Mon Mothma]], the [[Head of State/Legends|leader]] of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]], in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']].

